INSERT INTO "USER_REVIEW" ("RESTAURANT_ID","REVIEW_DATE","COMMENT","REVIEW_RATING")VALUES('25974184','2017-10-07','The food was GREAT and the service was fast. When you walk in the restaurant is divided into two halves, the first half is wooden tables and benches then when you go a little further in it''s more traditional tables and chairs. I would suggest going to the back section as the wooden benches weren''t very comfortable. I ordered the Schnitzel dish which came with potatoes two eggs and salad, everything down to the cabbage salad had an amazing taste. Everything was well seasoned and cooked and the portions were quite big. The price was decent, for two main plates and two sodas we paid a total of €24. It''s also quite easy to get to by transit. I definitely recommend this place.','4');
