INSERT INTO "USER_REVIEW" ("RESTAURANT_ID","REVIEW_DATE","COMMENT","REVIEW_RATING")VALUES('21873683','2017-12-16','This is one of the most famous but hidden places in the biggest village of Germany! The dancing location has a long term history of more than 100 years for dancing and party in the eastern part of Berlin. All the Berliners know the place by the name, but not everybody visit it. So actually it''s more famous to the tourists and all the trendy pseudo-hipsters from all over the world.
INSERT INTO "USER_REVIEW" ("RESTAURANT_ID","REVIEW_DATE","COMMENT","REVIEW_RATING")VALUES('21873683','2018-01-04','Nice and funny. For something different.. to live something you would never expect in Berlin. But you have to like ballads, German food or pizza. There is also another room where to eat that in general is more quiet and the location is just amazing. In the end I would say is a bit retro'' place but sometimes is nice to experience something different','5');
INSERT INTO "USER_REVIEW" ("RESTAURANT_ID","REVIEW_DATE","COMMENT","REVIEW_RATING")VALUES('21873683','2017-12-14','Full of character and characters, this location shows its age in the best way. Once busy the staff gets a bit swamped with orders yet they stayed friendly throughout. Food was tasty, music was great and dancing was fun. Had a great evening, highly recommended','5');
INSERT INTO "USER_REVIEW" ("RESTAURANT_ID","REVIEW_DATE","COMMENT","REVIEW_RATING")VALUES('21873683','2017-12-19','This is one of the coolest places I have seen so far in Berlin. The food is good and the portions are huge (seriously, you will not be disappointed and the pricepoint is also very fair), the service is quick and nice but what really makes this place is the nice and relaxed atmosphere amongst the countless people dancing on the dancefloor. The music at least when I was there was fitting and overall we had a very nice evening as a group. Five stars!','5');
