INSERT INTO "USER_REVIEW" ("RESTAURANT_ID","REVIEW_DATE","COMMENT","REVIEW_RATING")VALUES('38531921','2017-10-17','I was planning to meet up with a friend in the area of nortbahnhoff,  and while looking for vegetarian restaurants (common way to search and find vegan or vegan friendly places in Google maps) I found this place. While looking at their menu I realized that many of the dishes are possible to order with tofu - therefore vegan dishes are available. As we read the menu,  it stated on the bottom the different allergies. No mention of fish sauce... As we we''re about to order I asked about several dishes that we''re served with tofu, if they are vegan. Only than the waiter said that no dish is vegan only vegetarian (never knew that fish is not an animal), and that there is also no option to even make them vegan by request.  Left us no option to just get up and leave! I think this restaurant and it''s menu are misleading!  It should not come up as a vegetarian option in Google maps as well!','1');
INSERT INTO "USER_REVIEW" ("RESTAURANT_ID","REVIEW_DATE","COMMENT","REVIEW_RATING")VALUES('38531921','2017-07-04','I''ve lived in Berlin for a month but this is the first restaurant I''ve wanted to review. I dined in for dinner last night and ordered the seaweed salad and the mango curry with chicken. Both dishes were so fresh and flavorful. I had enough leftovers of both for lunch today. Service was quick and friendly. The prices are reasonable especially considering I had enough for a second meal. The atmosphere is great because it is slightly upscale but also cozy. So happy this is right in my neighborhood, I will definitely be back regularly. ','5');
