INSERT INTO "USER_REVIEW" ("RESTAURANT_ID","REVIEW_DATE","COMMENT","REVIEW_RATING")VALUES('93575769','2017-10-22','The venue itself is in remarkable place, with a great view on the Berlin panorama. Service was very kind and quite fast. Unfortunately if you take the food, and compare it to the prices you have to pay, you will get a disappointment. I know that the prices are high because of the place, but are clearly too high for this kind of quality of food. The food itself is tasty, but it is not shockingly great.','4');
INSERT INTO "USER_REVIEW" ("RESTAURANT_ID","REVIEW_DATE","COMMENT","REVIEW_RATING")VALUES('93575769','2017-06-20','Clearly one of the most exhilarating places to eat in Berlin. We visited the restaurant at the end of May with our son''s In Laws and had the most wonderful tea and cake on a perfect afternoon. For two English tea drinkers the brew was perfect and the apple cake absolutely lovely. We were not rushed and could stay as long as we wished. The service from the waitress was excellent. I would love to have an evening meal here to see the spectacular views at night. We would definitely visit again.','5');
